To create _both_ a new ARK NAAN and DOI prefix, follow these steps.
Don't follow these steps if you're only creating a DOI prefix or
only creating a NAAN.

1. run ./shdr_review
2. think
3. run ./shdr_prep  # this MINTS strings for shoulders, prefixes, and NAANs
4. think
5.1. on Mac run ./ezidnewacct      		# remind yourself of args
5.2. copy form letter ANVL into file 'newaccount.txt'
5.3. run ./ezidnewacct ARGS < newaccount.txt	# CREATES actual minters
5.4. copy and paste appropriate bits into appropriate files
6. consider running 'make' from /noid/naans
7. done
